{"tid":225543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普： 我願意會見北韓領導人金正恩，只要情勢正確","createTime":"2017-05-01T23:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T01:45:41.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a028c79be26c2c505c526867538a2f3296d2606d","tid":225543,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"狂人即將相見！ 川普：我願會見金正恩<br />\n<br />\n2017-05-02 01:34<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯陳正健／綜合報導〕美國總統川普1日再發驚人之語。他在接受《彭博新聞社》（Bloomberg News）訪問時宣稱，他願意會見北韓領導人金正恩，只要情勢正確。<br />\n<br />\n川普向《彭博新聞社》表示：「如果會見他（金正恩）對我是適當之事，我會絕對地，我會很榮幸地實行。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，川普也指出：「多數政治人物永遠不會道出此言，但我告訴你，在正確的情勢下，我願意見他（金正恩），我們有爆炸新聞。」<br />\n<br />\n其實，川普對與金正恩的形容措辭，每次都很有川式風格。上個月北韓試射飛彈時，川普曾要金正恩「乖一點」（Got to behave）。<br />\n<br />\n不久之前，川普在接受《哥倫比亞廣播公司》（CBS）採訪時，還稱讚金正恩是「聰明傢伙」（smart cookie），年紀輕輕便掌管整個國家。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"9a60cd86702f8b9708fe535b4ba5a3cb292cbb94","tid":225543,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d17ab4cc1377f7de929e0e862b2e25612744a7","tid":225543,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:47:07.000Z","msg":"將棋王軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa7f64f51b5ed72f366315ae97a09b08c051ef1","tid":225543,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:34:38.000Z","msg":"唔再透過第3者<br />\n自已直接親自出手"},{"pid":"c4f99604246b137bb838d4940b8bbe83ec455088","tid":225543,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:05:32.000Z","msg":"支那隻狗由我直接睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204ca6c3aae3a4fc2a3aca15f06480ad22690f88","tid":225543,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0